data.description: Home sweet home !!! With easy access to highways, shopping centers, Saint Cloud Lake front park (marina, pier,  Walking trail,  water splash, boat ramp, restaurant, gazebo and much more) schools, hospital, about 25 minutes from Medical City, Lake Nona, Disney parks we welcome you and your family to this absolutely beautiful spacious 2,807 SF home, 4 bedroom 2- 1/2 bath. As you walk into the house you are welcome by an open living room dining combo area, followed by a spacious kitchen with a generous cabinet space, island, equipped with microwave, stove, fridge, dishwasher and family Room with ceiling fan for all your parties and family entertainment. With a nice view to your back patio to enjoy morning coffee or evening wine surrounded by fresh herbs and some fruit plants. To the left, access your master suite offering a generous and spacious walk in closet follow by a nice garden tub and double sinks. Laundry room is located on the main floor near the kitchen. As accessing the second floor, you’ll find a loft that you can make your own family room, office, or whatever you wish, Follow by 3 bedrooms and a full bath. AC unit is located on the second floor. Roof installed 8/2021, water softener installed 2015, serviced  6/2023, water heater installed 6/9/2020, In & Out AC Unit installed 4/2021.This amazing  community has so much to offer. Come explore clubhouse with pool, fitness center key access , playgrounds, dog park, tennis court,basketball  and much more. Schedule your private tour today. This is a must see home !!!
